    "Afterward, we query the LLM to determine the next client requests that can affect the server's state.",
    "To mitigate the influence of the LLM's stochastic behavior, we prompted the LLM 100 times for each state.Figure 5 shows the results.",
    "Each pie chart demonstrates the results for each state.",
    "Each segment in each pie chart represents a distinct type of client request.",
    "The gray portion represents the percentage of client-request types that can lead to state change."
